60.7	Desertification	Desertification	Desertification is the degradation of land in any dryland. It is caused by a variety of factors, such as climate change and human activities, desertification is one of the most significant global environmental problems.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/Desertification_map.png/400px-Desertification_map.png
